name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Real Vision Scrape Utility for OneLook

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: For use by RVI OneLook customers to scrape data from the active tab to send to the locally installed RVI web server for data extraction and index assignment to documents per the customer's configuration.
